name: The Universal Mycelium
description: Everything in our reality is permeated with interweaving and interaction. Thoughts, images, words, actions are fungal spores that sprout when they get into the soil. Love, friendship, hatred, sex, attraction, disgust ... The universal mycelium, inside which there is a cycle. Symbiosis or parasitism. Selfishness or collaboration. The ring is a symbol of the cyclical and infinite nature of everything that happens. Sculpted in VR. 1260x1750 px. by Yalo 2021
